@NODE history "History"

Version 1.0  - Initial release.

Version 1.1  - Added version string
             - Now deletes the batch entry for the description file if it
               exists regardless of wether the user answers yes or no.

Version 1.2  - Changed name of description file to 'ZZDESC.BCH'.
             - Now tells the user they have files tagged before asking if
               they wish to download descriptions.

Version 2.0  - Changed program name from DDesc to Blitz-Download.
             - Added COPYCD code.
             - Can now get descriptions for all tagged files which are tagged
               with the M-Tag package, if the tagged file has a filenote, or
               if the file is a private file.

@ENDNODE
